  "snippet": "In which I finally finish the book, the Grail Knight reaches Corbenic, the king is healed, the Waste Land lives again and Doris gets her oats ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏ ͏",
